                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="3" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> et memoriae aeternae <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> Marti Valeri qui et <lb n="3"/>Viventi vano signo <lb n="4"/>cognominatus ani<lb break="no" n="5"/>mae innocentissi<lb break="no" n="6"/>mae et infanti dulcis<lb break="no" n="7"/>simo et desiderantissi<lb break="no" n="8"/>mo non solum a paren<lb break="no" n="9"/>tibus sed et ab amicis qui <lb n="10"/>amissionem eiius <note>sic</note> flagi<lb break="no" n="11"/>tant <expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ui</ex></expan> vixit annis VI <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ense</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iebus</ex></expan> X ut subita valetudin<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> <lb n="13"/>sit abreptus <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Martius <lb n="14"/>Toutedo et Mercator <lb n="15"/>Ateurita parentes mi<lb break="no" n="16"/>serrimi amisso filio <lb n="17"/><expan><abbr>fecer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan> et sibi vivi posue<lb break="no" n="18"/>runt et sub ascia dedika<lb break="no" n="19"/>verunt <note>sic</note> bene vale <lb n="20"/>anima dulcissima
